T02D2608:81a-1: ya m'a ri k'a la s'a dha na n'a ma /
T02D2608:81a-3: gshin rje dgra nag po'i sgrub thabs zhes bya ba /
T02D2608:81a-4: bcom ldan 'das shes rab ye shes la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2608:81a-5: log pa'i lta ba gcod mdzad cing //
T02D2608:81a-6: shes rab snying rjes rab tu khros //
T02D2608:81a-7: mche ba gtsigs shing bzhad mdzad pa //
T02D2608:81a-8: gshin rje'i dgra la phyag 'tshal nas //
T02D2608:81a-9: rgyud chen sgyu 'phrul dra ba las //
T02D2608:81a-10: bla ma'i man ngag la brten nas //
T02D2608:81a-11: bdag gis sgrub pa'i rim pa bzhin //
T02D2608:81a-12: sgrub la phan phyir brtsam par bya //
T02D2608:81b-0: bden zhing me tog gcal @81b bkram pa'i //
T02D2608:81b-1: bde ba'i stan la nyer 'dug ste //
T02D2608:81b-2: lha dang dkon mchog spyan drangs nas //
T02D2608:81b-3: mchod dang sdig bshags la sogs bya //
T02D2608:81b-4: aa bh'a ba sva bh'a ba bi shuddha badzra tsakshu aa a'a aam aa:/
T02D2608:81b-5: de nas stong pa'i ting nge 'dzin las //
T02D2608:81b-6: nam mkhar aa ni bsam par bya //
T02D2608:81b-7: rdo rje me dpung rab tu 'phros //
T02D2608:81b-8: rdo rje'i steng du aa bsams te //
T02D2608:81b-9: gyur bas shes rab ye shes ni //
T02D2608:81b-12: gyur pas gshin rje gshed po ni //
T02D2608:81b-13: bgegs kyi rgyal po chen po ste //
T02D2608:81b-14: lus ni rdo rjes rnam par brgyan //
T02D2608:81b-15: phyag na rdo rje be con dang //
T02D2608:81b-16: shugs dang bcas pa'i sprul zhags bsnams //
T02D2608:81b-17: tshang med bzhi ldan khro bo ni //
T02D2608:81b-18: shin tu khros pa rnam par bsgom //
T02D2608:81b-19: dza: h'um bam ho: zhes bya bas dgug pa dang gzhug pa dang /
T02D2608:81b-23: gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs nas dbang bskur bya'o //
T02D2608:81b-24: de nas bsgoms pas skyon bzlas pa bya ste /
T02D2608:81b-25: aom pra dzny'adzny'a na m'u rta ye ya m'anta ka h'um /
T02D2608:81b-27: mtshan brjod de gtor ma gtang bar bya'o //
T02D2608:81b-28: de ltar bstod nas gshegs su gsol lo //
T02D2608:81b-29: bdag gis 'gro ba phan phyir brtsams //
T02D2608:81b-30: dge bas 'bras bu tshad med shog / gshin rje
T02D2608:81b-31: gshed kyi sgrub thabs slob dpon aa shva ka shr'i
T02D2608:81b-34: // / pandi ta dharma shr'i mi tra dang //
